    is dead - play somethin else abashi aint listening]</i></font><br>
    <br>
    Listening, just not commenting any more. Ive posted in several ranger
    threads since the boards were converted, and each post led to follow-up
    flames, personal attacks, profanity, and other things that are no longer
    allowed on these boards. Class-specific threads in general are very
    inflamatory since people are very passionate about what they play, so Ill
    probably not be commenting in those threads very much unless I can add
    something positive to them, rather than constantly telling them no.</li>
