    <font color="#072876"><i>[Quote from original post: When the forum_faq came
    out and I saw theyd removed the initials for Role Play, calling EverQuest a
    MMOG (as opposed to MMORPG), it just confirmed what I already knew]</i></font><br>
    <br>
    Youre reading a bit too much into it.<br>
    <br>
    And MMOG is just a broader description of what we make. Yes, EverQuest is an
    MMORPG. Sovereign will be a MMORTS. We have a MMOAG (action game) in
    development that we havent announced yet (other than the fact that we have
    one in development). We have a couple other MMORPGs in development as well.
    Whether MMORPG, MMORTS, MMOAG, or MMO-anything, they are all MMOGs, and
    thats what we do.<br>
