  <li><a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/everquest/Forum2/HTML/010379.html"><b>Ports
    On Single Players</b></a><br>
    <font color="#072876"><i>[Quote from original post: Abashi... is it possible
    to make ports castable on single players?]</i></font><br>
    <br>
    It is possible to do this, however its not really what we had in mind for
    teleportation. Wizards and Druids are supposed to take others to the
    destination, not send them to the destination. The power of teleportation is
    in the druid/wizard, and they just have the ability to extend their aura, if
    you will, to include others.<br>
    <br>
    Its not likely that we would implement this.</li>
