    world via an optional two hour patch :P that would let us explore the new
    zone? Kudos on Paineel and recently The Hole.]</i></font><br>
    <br>
    We do have additional free zones planned, with the Warrens being the next
    one on the list. Ill have to check on Tuesday to see how this is coming
    along. I think that it will still be a few weeks before well see this go
    live.<br>
    <br>
    <font color="#072876"><i>[Quote from original post: 2) If you do implement a
    new zone, could you please just announce &quot;A new zone is available via
    the optional patch, and that no new information is to be released about this
    area. Explore!]</i></font><br>
