    up on the Test server :)<br>
    <br>
    <font color="#072876"><i>[Quote from original post: There are no new zones
    for the lower levels. Can you bring this up at the next tuning meeting??
    (Please?)]</i></font><br>
    <br>
    The issue here is that there is already a vast number of areas for the lower
    level folks out there. They are not the ones who are running out of content.
    Furthermore, since they are low level, they progress rather quickly from one
    set of zones to another, meaning that enjoyment of any new specifically
    low-level zone would be fleeting. Its the mid and upper levels that are
    typically most in need of new content.<br>
    <br>
